            <section>
                <h2>Type 1 Diabetes</h2>
                <p>Type 1 Diabetes is an autoimmune condition in which the immune system 
                    is activated to desotry the cells in the pancreas which produce insulin. 
                    Type 1 Diabetes is not linked to modifiable lifestyle factors. There is 
                    no cure and it cannot be prevented. </p>
                    
                    <p>Consult your doctor if you notice any <a href ="https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/type-1-diabetes/symptoms-causes/syc-20353011">symptoms</a> in you or your child. 
                </p>
            </section>
